  {
    "uuid": "38361732-71f5-5a48-a2b5-a7182e4b2a9f",
    "entry": "願酒",
    "reading": {
      "primary": "がんしゅ",
      "alternatives": [],
      "is_heteronym": false
    },
    "grammar": {
      "pos": [
        "名詞"
      ],
      "ctype": null,
      "inflections": null
    },
    "definitions": [
      {
        "index": 1,
        "gloss": "praying at a temple or shrine for help to stop drinking",
        "register": "standard",
        "nuance": null,
        "scenarios": [],
        "sensory_tags": {
          "colors": [],
          "temperature": null,
          "sounds": [],
          "emotions": []
        },
        "collocations": [],
        "examples": {
          "standard": [
            {
              "text": "「お父さん、また隠れて飲んでるんじゃない？ せっかく神社で願酒をして誓ったのに！」",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-3-flash-preview"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "酒で身を滅ぼしかけた彼は、最後の手段として断酒の神様に願酒を行い、以来一滴も杯を口にしていない。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-3-flash-preview"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "三年にわたる願酒の期間を無事に終えた彼は、見違えるほど健康的で活動的な生活を取り戻した。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-3-flash-preview"
              }
            }
          ],
          "literary": []
        }
      }
    ],
